draw_mod - Simple framebuffer test module for QEMU virt

Allocates a 640x480x32 framebuffer (vzalloc) and exposes
it via /proc/test_gui. Minimal test to verify virtio-gpu
framebuffer access from kernel space.

Build:
  make -C /path/to/kernel M=$(pwd) \
    ARCH=arm64 CROSS_COMPILE=aarch64-linux-gnu-

Files:
  test_simple.c  — module source
  Makefile       — kbuild
